# web site design for selling shirts 
uses java script jQuery

you have multiple options for your order 
-color 
-style
-Qualtiy of fabric
-quatity
 the user use this options to choose a product that is a part of object containing all products availble
 then the total price is calculated 
 
 1. The prices above are for Basic quality (q150). 
 The high quality shirt (190g/m2) has a 12% increase in the unit price.

 2. Apply the following discounts for higher quantities: 
-1: above 1.000 units - 20% discount
-2: above 500 units - 12% discount
-3: above 100 units - 5% discount